        Your spot is confirmed. Here's what you've unlocked.
      </p>

      <div class="ty-benefits">
        <div class="ty-card">
          <div class="ty-card-icon">🏷️</div>
          <div>
            <p class="ty-card-title text-h3">
              Guaranteed Super Early Bird Pricing
            </p>
            <p class="ty-card-desc text-p">
              The best price the DP-M2 will ever have. No surprises, just the
              best deal.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ty-card">
          <div class="ty-card-icon">🚚</div>
