            <p class="ty-card-title text-h3">VIP Backstage Pass</p>
            <p class="ty-card-desc text-p">
              Behind the scenes content, early announcements, and insider-only
              updates. You'll know everything before it goes public.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
